		<div id="comment_body_64190962"><p>Would be possible to detect the signal direction and ignore anything that comes from ground? Maybe some kind of unidirectional antennas pointed to known satellite positions?<br>Also, would GPS satellites digitally sign the signal? That'd be another way to certify the signal origin.</p></div>
	</div>

